articles.title: Space telescope spots high-speed winds blasted from massive black hole - Interesting Engineering
articles.description: The European Space Agency's (ESA) XMM-Newton observed this peculiar activity in a spiral galaxy known as Markarian 817.
articles.content:
Interestingly, despite the powerful gravitational forces, black holes do not consume all of the gas swirling toward them.
